Hi all,
I've setup a firewall using Linux IP filtering rules, with kernel 2.0.36. 
Everything seems to work, except PPTP.
I've allowed unrestricted traffic through the firewall to the PPTP server, 
port TCP/1723. But the firewall keeps blocking packets of type 47. Is there 
any way to allow those packets ? IPFWADM doesn't seem to know about those...
Any help appreciated, I have some not-so-happy users...
